	<script type="text/javascript">
	window.G = {"conf" : {"windowSize" : 0}};

	var viewport = window.innerWidth || document.documentElement.clientWidth || document.body.clientWidth,
		stage = document.getElementById('zaz-gambit'),
		reducePage = false;

	if (viewport < 1024) {
		stage.setAttribute('class', 'w768');
		window.G.conf.windowSize = 768;
	} else if (viewport < 1280) {
		if(reducePage === true){
			stage.setAttribute('class', 'w768');
			window.G.conf.windowSize = 768;
		}else{
			stage.setAttribute('class', 'w1024');
			window.G.conf.windowSize = 1024;
		}
	} else if (viewport >= 1280) {
		if(reducePage === true){
			stage.setAttribute('class', 'w1024');
			window.G.conf.windowSize = 1024;
		}else{
			stage.setAttribute('class', 'w1280');
			window.G.conf.windowSize = 1280;
		}
	}
	</script><noscript>Scripts de configurações</noscript>

(function() {
    'use strict';
    if (!window.zaz || typeof window.zaz.use != 'function') {
        throw new Error('Framework not found as "window.zaz".');
    }
    window.zaz.use(function(pkg) {
        try {
            if (typeof pkg.includer != 'object') {
                throw new Error('Includer not delivered on this pkg');
            }
            if (includerComponents.length > 0) {
                pkg.includer.registerFetchedComponents(includerComponents[0].components);
            }
        } catch (e) {
            e.message = 'Error on Includer\'s reporter: ' + e.messsage;
            if (window.console && typeof window.console.error == 'function') {
                window.console.error(e);
            }
        }
    });
})();

.agrupamento-vertical-simples .glb-hl-style-informe-publicitario .chapeu {
    color: #fff !important;
}

.nano>.pane {
    z-index: 12;
}
</style><script type="text/javascript">
(function() {
    'use strict';

    var timerId ; // Current timer handler
    var refreshTime = 300000; // 1000*60*5
    var graceTimerStep = 10000; // 1000*10

    var isMobile = function() {
        return ($('#regua-navegacao:visible').length > 0);
    };

    var preparePlayer = function(player) {

        var refreshPageWithTimeout = function() {

            console.log('Trying to refresh on' + graceTimerStep + ' ms.');
            setTimeout(function() {
                    if (!player.isPlaying()) {
                        refreshPage();
                    }
                    console.log('Watching a video. Refresh the page later');
                }, graceTimerStep);
        };

        var playerComplete = player.complete;
        if ($.isFunction(playerComplete)) {
            player.complete = function() {
                playerComplete.apply(this, arguments);
                refreshPage();
            };
        }
        else {
            player.complete = refreshPage;
        }

        var playerOnPause = player.onPause;
        if ($.isFunction(playerOnPause)) {
            player.onPause = function() {
                playerOnPause.apply(this, arguments);
                refreshPageWithTimeout(player);
            };
        }
        else {
            player.onPause = refreshPageWithTimeout;
        }

        var playerOnStop = player.onStop;
        if ($.isFunction(playerOnStop)) {
            player.onStop = function() {
              playerOnStop.apply(this, arguments);
              refreshPageWithTimeout();
          };
        }
        else {
            player.onStop = refreshPageWithTimeout;
        }
    };

    var refreshPage = function() {
        if (!isMobile()) {
            console.log('Refreshing now');
            window.location.reload();
        }
        else {
            console.log('Is mobile: Not reloading the page.');
        }
    };

    var checkForVideoPlaying = function() {

        console.log('Timeout: Refreshing the page at any moment.');

        clearTimeout(timerId); // clear timer

        var isVideoPlaying = false;

        $.each(WM.PlayerManager, function(index, player) {
            isVideoPlaying = isVideoPlaying || player.isPlaying();
            if (player.isPlaying()) {
                preparePlayer(player);
            }
        });

        if (!isVideoPlaying) {
            refreshPage();
        }

    };

    var startTimer = function() {
        timerId = setTimeout(checkForVideoPlaying, refreshTime);
    };

    window.onload= function() {
         if (!isMobile() && window.location.hash != '#debug' ) {
            console.log('Time Started: ' + refreshTime + ' ms until Refresh.');
            startTimer();
        }
     }
})();
</script></body><!-- Página gerada em 28/03/2017 21:06:02 --></html>

                    }
                }
            };
            postJquerySetup();
        })();
    </script><section data-track-category="cards" data-track-action="lista" class="gui-card card-lista"><header class="gui-card-title gui-color-primary-bg"><h1 class="gui-text-title"><p class="">VARIEDADES</p></h1></header><section class="gui-card-content"><div class="nano"><div class="content nano-content"><a href="http://g1.globo.com/pernambuco/noticia/espetaculo-premiado-no-janeiro-de-grandes-espetaculos-volta-a-ser-encenado-no-recife.ghtml" title="Peça premiada volta a ser encenada (Mariá Vilar/Divulgação)" class="card-lista-item-wide-link"><div class="card-lista-item-wide gui-image-hover"><figure data-track-click="clique | thumb imagem | posicao 1"

(function() {
    'use strict';

    var timerId ; // Current timer handler
    var refreshTime = 300000; // 1000*60*5
    var graceTimerStep = 10000; // 1000*10

    var isMobile = function() {
        return ($('#regua-navegacao:visible').length > 0);
    };

    var preparePlayer = function(player) {

        var refreshPageWithTimeout = function() {

            console.log('Trying to refresh on' + graceTimerStep + ' ms.');
            setTimeout(function() {
                    if (!player.isPlaying()) {
                        refreshPage();
                    }
                    console.log('Watching a video. Refresh the page later');
                }, graceTimerStep);
        };

        var playerComplete = player.complete;
        if ($.isFunction(playerComplete)) {
            player.complete = function() {
                playerComplete.apply(this, arguments);
                refreshPage();
            };
        }
        else {
            player.complete = refreshPage;
        }

        var playerOnPause = player.onPause;
        if ($.isFunction(playerOnPause)) {
            player.onPause = function() {
                playerOnPause.apply(this, arguments);
                refreshPageWithTimeout(player);
            };
        }
        else {
            player.onPause = refreshPageWithTimeout;
        }

        var playerOnStop = player.onStop;
        if ($.isFunction(playerOnStop)) {
            player.onStop = function() {
              playerOnStop.apply(this, arguments);
              refreshPageWithTimeout();
          };
        }
        else {
            player.onStop = refreshPageWithTimeout;
        }
    };

    var refreshPage = function() {
        if (!isMobile()) {
            console.log('Refreshing now');
            window.location.reload();
        }
        else {
            console.log('Is mobile: Not reloading the page.');
        }
    };

    var checkForVideoPlaying = function() {

        console.log('Timeout: Refreshing the page at any moment.');

        clearTimeout(timerId); // clear timer

        var isVideoPlaying = false;

        $.each(WM.PlayerManager, function(index, player) {
            isVideoPlaying = isVideoPlaying || player.isPlaying();
            if (player.isPlaying()) {
                preparePlayer(player);
            }
        });

        if (!isVideoPlayi
